                'directions_legacy' => 'Dough:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>Mix the flour, yeast, salt and sugar in a bowl. Then, add the powdered milk and baking powder. Make a hole in the middle, and pour the oil into it. Stir and add water as needed to form a soft dough. If the dough is too stiff, add more water. Put the dough into an oiled bowl and let it rest for 2 hours.</li>
