                'id' => 1926,
            'title' => 'Squared Meat Pies (Lahm Bi Ajin Sarej)',
                'slug' => 'squared-meat-pies-lahm-bi-ajin-sarej',
                'content' => 'Here is a delicious and easy recipe to prepare Lahm Bi Ajin, to taste even better that the ones you order from outside. They have a unique mix of flavors and are perfect for a late breakfast or a quick lunch. Serve them with yogurt for a yummy taste.',
                'time' => '30',
                'serve' => '15',
