                'slug' => 'shrimps-and-pineapple-fried-rice',
                'content' => 'A fried rice dish made with shrimps and pineapple. An amazing combination of sweet and savory that turn this simple dish into a flavorful meal everyone will love. Prepare it step by step with Sousou.',
