                'slug' => 'kibbeh-nayyeh',
                'content' => 'When we say traditional Lebanese mezze, the first thing that comes to our mind is kibbeh nayyeh. It’s a beloved Lebanese dish made of raw meat and burghul. Sprinkle some olive oil and dry mint over the top before serving.',
