                'directions' => '[{"direction":"Wash the cracked wheat and let it sit for 15 minutes. Using a food processor, mash the onion and cracked wheat for 5 minutes.  Then, add salt, pepper and marjoram. Next, add the meat along with 3 or 4 cubes of ice. Mash the ingredients for another 5 minutes.","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b79"},{"direction":"Remove the mixture and knead it with wet hands for 7 minutes until it\'s soft.","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b78"},{"direction":"Place the kibbeh nayyeh on a plate. Decorate it with fresh mint.","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b77"},{"direction":"It can be served with olive oil, green onions, radish and fresh mint.","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b76"}]',
            'ingredients' => '[{"name":"fresh lamb ground meat","quantity":"\\u00bd    Kg","subIngredients":"","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b7f"},{"name":"fine cracked wheat (burghul)","quantity":"1     Cup","subIngredients":"","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b7e"},{"name":"\\u23ab\\tBig onion","quantity":"1","subIngredients":"","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b7d"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":"\\u00bd    Teaspoon","subIngredients":"","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b7c"},{"name":"marjoram","quantity":"\\u00bd    Teaspoon","subIngredients":"","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b7b"},{"name":"Salt to taste","quantity":"","subIngredients":"","_id":"5a44b16f13e3cd4c649f0b7a"}]',
                'directions_legacy' => '<ul>
<li>Wash the cracked wheat and let it sit for 15 minutes. Using a food processor, mash the onion and cracked wheat for 5 minutes. Then, add salt, pepper and marjoram. Next, add the meat along with 3 or 4 cubes of ice. Mash the ingredients for another 5 minutes.</li>
