<li>Add 5 cups of water with 3 tablespoons of tomato paste. Let it simmer on low heat for 20 minutes or until it has thickened. Once thickened, add the pasta &amp; mix. Then, add the cubed tomatoes, green pepper &amp; half of the cheese, making sure to mix well.</li>
