                'directions_legacy' => 'Chicken:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>In a bowl, marinate the chicken ingredients overnight</li>
<li>The next day, place the chicken and marinade in a Pyrex and bake in the oven until golden brown.</li>
</ul>
&nbsp;

