<ul>
<li>3 Onions, diced</li>
<li>3 Garlic cloves, diced</li>
<li>400g Fresh spinach, chopped</li>
<li>1 Tablespoon oregano</li>
<li>Salt &amp; pepper</li>
<li>3 Tablespoons olive oil</li>
<li>300g Feta cheese</li>
<li>2 Tomatoes, diced</li>
</ul>
&nbsp;

Dough:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>3 Cups flour</li>
<li>1 Teaspoon instant yeast</li>
<li>¼ Teaspoon sugar</li>
<li>¼ Teaspoon salt</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons olive oil</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons powdered milk</li>
<li>½ to ¾ Cup warm water</li>
</ul>',
