                'directions_legacy' => 'Cake:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>Beat the eggs, sugar, vanilla and lemon rind with an electric mixer in a bowl for 5 to 6 minutes.</li>
<li>Beat the butter in a separate bowl, until it becomes creamy.</li>
<li>Stir in the flour using a spatula. Then add the coffee and baking powder.</li>
<li>Pour the mixture into a buttered pan.</li>
<li>Bake in the oven at 200 degrees C. for 40 minutes.</li>
<li>Unmold the cake into a plate.</li>
</ul>
