                'title' => 'White Beans Stew with Rice',
                'slug' => 'white-beans-stew-with-rice',
                'content' => 'Here\'s another Sousou stew for you and your beloved family! White beans and meat chops are an absolute protein boost. Here\'s how the Lebanese people enjoy it the most!',
                'time' => '50',
                'serve' => '6',
                'video' => '',
                'directions' => '[{"direction":"WHITE BEANS STEW","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b26"},{"direction":"Soak the beans overnight with boiled water. The following day, put the beans into a pot and cover with water. Let it boil for 10 minutes, then, strain them.","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b25"},{"direction":"Fry the onions and garlic, in the high pressure cooker until golden. Then, add the meat and fry until its color changes. Next, add the diced tomatoes and let simmer for 10 minutes. Lastly, add the beans, salt, pepper, tomato paste and a cinnamon stick.","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b24"},{"direction":"Cover with water and cook in the high pressure cooker for half an hour.","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b23"},{"direction":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b22"},{"direction":"RICE","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b21"},{"direction":"Soak the two types of rice in water for half an hour before cooking.","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b20"},{"direction":"Fry the vermicelli until golden, then, add the rice, salt and water.","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b1f"},{"direction":"Once it starts boiling, reduce the heat & cook until all water evaporates.","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b1e"}]',
                'ingredients' => '[{"name":"WHITE BEANS STEW","quantity":"bold","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b36"},{"name":"Cup small dried white beans","quantity":"1","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b35"},{"name":"lamb or beef cubes","quantity":"200 g","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b34"},{"name":"Big onion, diced","quantity":"1","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b33"},{"name":"Medium soft red tomatoes, diced","quantity":"2","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b32"},{"name":"Garlic cloves , cut into round pieces","quantity":"6","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b31"},{"name":"tomato paste","quantity":"2    Tablespoons","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b30"},{"name":"Cinnamon stick","quantity":"1","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b2f"},{"name":"Salt and pepper to taste","quantity":"","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b2e"},{"name":"","quantity":"","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b2d"},{"name":"RICE","quantity":"bold","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b2c"},{"name":"Egyptian rice","quantity":"1 cup","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b2b"},{"name":"Uncle Ben\\u2019s rice","quantity":"1 cup","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b2a"},{"name":"vermicelli","quantity":"\\u00bd cup","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b29"},{"name":"water","quantity":"1\\u00be    cups","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b28"},{"name":"salt to taste","quantity":"","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c90210f385c43042512b27"}]',
                'directions_legacy' => '<ul>
<li>WHITE BEANS STEW</li>
<li>Soak the beans overnight with boiled water. The following day, put the beans into a pot and cover with water. Let it boil for 10 minutes, then, strain them.</li>
<li>Fry the onions and garlic, in the high pressure cooker until golden. Then, add the meat and fry until its color changes. Next, add the diced tomatoes and let simmer for 10 minutes. Lastly, add the beans, salt, pepper, tomato paste and a cinnamon stick.</li>
<li>Cover with water and cook in the high pressure cooker for half an hour.</li>
<li></li>
<li>RICE</li>
<li>Soak the two types of rice in water for half an hour before cooking.</li>
<li>Fry the vermicelli until golden, then, add the rice, salt and water.</li>
<li>Once it starts boiling, reduce the heat &amp; cook until all water evaporates.</li>
</ul>',
                'ingredients_legacy' => 'White beans stew:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>1 Cup small dried white beans</li>
<li>200g Lamb or beef cubes</li>
<li>1 Big onion, diced</li>
<li>2 Medium soft red tomatoes, diced</li>
<li>6 Garlic cloves , cut into round pieces</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons tomato paste</li>
<li>1 Cinnamon stick</li>
<li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
</ul>
Rice:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>1 Cup egyptian rice</li>
<li>1 Cup Uncle Ben’s rice</li>
<li>½ Cup vermicelli</li>
<li>1¾ Cups water</li>
<li>Salt to taste</li>
</ul>',
