                'directions_legacy' => '<div class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-scope">Cookies:</span></div>
<div></div>
<ul>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">Combine the milk, butter &amp; sugar in a saucepan and stir on low heat until the butter melts and the sugar dissolves.</span></li>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">Place the flour into a bowl. Then, add fenugreek, musk, nutmeg, baking powder &amp; yeast. Next, add the orange blossom water. Lastly, add the milk and butter mixture. Combine and knead the dough by hand.</span></li>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">Cover with a nylon sheet and a dry kitchen towel and let it rest for 2 hours.</span></li>
</ul>
<div class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-scope"> </span></div>
<div class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">With pistachio and walnuts:</span></div>
<div></div>
<ul>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">Grind pistachios in a food processor and mix it with the remaining filling ingredients.</span></li>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">Repeat the same procedure for the walnuts filling.</span></li>
</ul>
<div class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-scope"> </span></div>
<div class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-scope">With dates:
</span></div>
<div></div>
<ul>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">In a tray, place the dates with the butter and put it in the oven until the butter melts. Then grind them in a food processor.</span></li>
</ul>
<div class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-scope"> </span></div>
<div class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-scope">Filled Cookies:
</span></div>
<div></div>
<ul>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">Divide the dough into small balls. Flatten it in the palm of your hand. Then stuff it with 1 teaspoon of the filling. Seal the edges and roll it into a ball.</span></li>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">Form the dough into the shapes you prefer. You can choose two different shapes in order to differentiate them from each other (depending on the filling).</span></li>
<li class="ng-scope"><span class="method ng-binding ng-scope" style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; vertical-align: middle;">Place them onto a tray and bake them in the oven until golden brown.</span></li>
</ul>',
