                'slug' => 'stuffed-mini-kibbeh-with-basil',
                'content' => 'Sousou\'s creativity knows no limit! Check out how she excelled in recreating your favorite kebbeh recipe! What a mix!',
                'time' => '60',
                'serve' => '30',
