                'title' => 'Lasagna with Eggplants',
                'slug' => 'lasagna-with-eggplants',
                'content' => 'It\'s your chance to learn how to make the best green lasagna with eggplant and robust Gruyere!',
                'time' => '30',
                'serve' => '8',
                'video' => '',
                'directions' => '[{"direction":"Fry the eggplants with oil and place in a strainer. Set aside.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321af"},{"direction":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321ae"},{"direction":"TOMATO SAUCE:","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321ad"},{"direction":"In a pot on the stove, fry the onions and garlic with oil until golden. Then, add the carrots and leeks and stir until cooked. Next, add the tomatoes. Dissolve the magi cube in water and add to the tomatoes. Lastly add tomato paste, oregano, salt and pepper.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321ac"},{"direction":"Let simmer on low heat until it thickens.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321ab"},{"direction":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321aa"},{"direction":"WHITE SAUCE:","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a9"},{"direction":"Place the flour in a pot and gradually add milk while constantly stirring.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a8"},{"direction":"Place the pot on the stove. Stir the milk until it thickens. Then, add the nutmeg, white pepper & salt.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a7"},{"direction":"Cut the feta cheese into pieces, grind it with the fresh cream in a food processor, and add them to the white sauce.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a6"},{"direction":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a5"},{"direction":"LASAGNA :","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a4"},{"direction":"Pour some of the white sauce into a Pyrex.  Next, place one layer of the green lasagna. Cover the lasagna with half of the tomato sauce and half of the fried eggplants. Then, add some cheese and some white sauce.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a3"},{"direction":"Repeat the same procedure to make another layer of lasagna. Lastly, cover with the third layer of lasagna and add the remaining white sauce over it along with the gruyere cheese.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a2"},{"direction":"Bake in oven until cheese melts.","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321a1"}]',
                'ingredients' => '[{"name":"Green Lasagna","quantity":"12 Pieces","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321c6"},{"name":"Eggplants, peeled and cut into round pieces","quantity":"3  Big","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321c5"},{"name":"shredded Gruyere Cheese","quantity":"300 Grams","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321c4"},{"name":"","quantity":"","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321c3"},{"name":"TOMATO SAUCE","quantity":"sauce","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321c2"},{"name":"Onions, diced","quantity":"2 Mediums","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321c1"},{"name":"Garlic cloves, smashed","quantity":"2","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321c0"},{"name":"Carrot, diced","quantity":"1","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321bf"},{"name":"Leek, chopped","quantity":"\\u00be  Cup","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321be"},{"name":"Tomatoes, peeled and diced","quantity":"1 Kg","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321bd"},{"name":"Oil","quantity":"3 Tablespoons","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321bc"},{"name":"Water","quantity":"1 Cup","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321bb"},{"name":"Magi","quantity":"1 Cube","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321ba"},{"name":"Tomato Paste","quantity":"1 Tablespoon","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b9"},{"name":"Oregano","quantity":"1 Tablespoon","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b8"},{"name":"Salt and pepper","quantity":"","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b7"},{"name":"","quantity":"","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b6"},{"name":"WHITE SAUCE","quantity":"bold","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b5"},{"name":"Milk","quantity":"4 Cups","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b4"},{"name":"Flour","quantity":"2 Tablespoons","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b3"},{"name":"Salt, white pepper and nutmeg","quantity":"","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b2"},{"name":"Feta Cheese","quantity":"200   Grams","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b1"},{"name":"Fresh Cream","quantity":"500 ml","subIngredients":"","_id":"59c3b6c03c56e6598b9321b0"}]',
                'directions_legacy' => '<ul>
<li>Fry the eggplants with oil and place in a strainer. Set aside.</li>
</ul>
&nbsp;

Tomato Sauce:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>In a pot on the stove, fry the onions and garlic with oil until golden. Then, add the carrots and leeks and stir until cooked. Next, add the tomatoes. Dissolve the magi cube in water and add to the tomatoes. Lastly add tomato paste, oregano, salt and pepper.</li>
<li>Let simmer on low heat until it thickens.</li>
</ul>
&nbsp;

White Sauce:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>Place the flour in a pot and gradually add milk while constantly stirring.</li>
<li>Place the pot on the stove. Stir the milk until it thickens. Then, add the nutmeg, white pepper &amp; salt.</li>
<li>Cut the feta cheese into pieces, grind it with the fresh cream in a food processor, and add them to the white sauce.</li>
</ul>
&nbsp;

Lasagna:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>Pour some of the white sauce into a Pyrex. Next, place one layer of the green lasagna. Cover the lasagna with half of the tomato sauce and half of the fried eggplants. Then, add some cheese and some white sauce.</li>
<li>Repeat the same procedure to make another layer of lasagna. Lastly, cover with the third layer of lasagna and add the remaining white sauce over it along with the gruyere cheese.</li>
<li>Bake in oven until cheese melts.</li>
</ul>',
                'ingredients_legacy' => '<ul>
<li>12 Pieces green lasagna</li>
<li>3 Big eggplants, peeled and cut into round pieces</li>
<li>300 Grams shredded gruyere cheese</li>
<li>Tomato sauce</li>
<li>2 Mediums onions, diced</li>
<li>2 Garlic cloves, smashed</li>
<li>1 Carrot, diced</li>
<li>¾ Cup leek, chopped</li>
<li>1 Kg Tomatoes, peeled and diced</li>
<li>3 Tablespoons oil</li>
<li>1 Cup water</li>
<li>1 Cube magi</li>
<li>1 Tablespoon tomato paste</li>
<li>1 Tablespoon oregano</li>
<li>Salt and pepper</li>
</ul>
White sauce:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>4 Cups milk</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons flour</li>
<li>Salt, white pepper and nutmeg</li>
<li>200 Grams feta cheese</li>
<li>500 ml Fresh cream</li>
</ul>',
