                'directions_legacy' => 'Meat:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>In a pot on the stove, fry the onions with oil until they change color. Then, add the meat and stir until the water evaporates. Next, add salt, black pepper, sumac and oregano. Lastly, add the water and tomato paste. Let simmer on low heat until the mixture thickens.</li>
