<ul>
<li>4 Red sweet peppers, diced</li>
<li>4 Large onions, cubed</li>
<li>1 Kg Jumbo shrimps</li>
<li>1 Kg Medium shrimps</li>
</ul>
&nbsp;

Sauce:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>4 Tablespoons coconut powder, dissolved in one cup of water</li>
<li>1 Cube Magi chicken broth, dissolved in one cup of water</li>
<li>1 Tablespoon mustard (moutarde à l’ancienne)</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons soy sauce</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons corn flour</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons concentrated hot pepper</li>
<li>1 Liter fresh cream</li>
</ul>
&nbsp;

Rice:

&nbsp;
<ul>
