<li>1 Teaspoon cardamom powder</li>
<li>3 Cups Uncle Ben’s rice</li>
<li>3 ¾ Cups water</li>
<li>Salt to taste</li>
</ul>
&nbsp;

Decoration:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>1 Cup chopped coriander</li>
<li>6 Spring onions, cut small</li>
<li>½ Cup chopped basil</li>
</ul>',
