<li>1 Bunch parsley</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons flour</li>
<li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
</ul>
Sauce:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>4 Onions sliced thin</li>
<li>3 Red &amp; soft tomatoes, diced</li>
<li>1 Tablespoon corn oil</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons tomato paste</li>
<li>1 Cinnamon stick</li>
<li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
<li>5 Cups water</li>
</ul>
Rice:

&nbsp;
<ul>
<li>½ Cup Egyptian Rice</li>
<li>½ Cup Uncle Benz Rice</li>
<li>½ Cup vermicelli</li>
<li>1 ¾ Cup water</li>
<li>Salt to taste</li>
</ul>',
