<li>1/2 Pack onion soup</li>
<li>200g Gruyere cheese, grated</li>
<li>4 Cloves garlic, chopped</li>
<li>½ Pack onion soup</li>
<li>½ Kg Tomatoes, peeled</li>
<li>1 Teaspoon saffron</li>
<li>½ Cup water</li>
<li>Salt And pepper to taste</li>
<li>2 Tablespoons corn oil</li>
</ul>',
